"{\"uid\": \"livenowfox.com-news-team-usa-uniform-olympics-opening-ceremonies-blue-jeans-ralph-lauren\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Here are the times in history when the Olympics have been canceled or postponed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 87, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NEW YORK-When Team USA walks among the world's best athletes at theParis Olympics' opening ceremonies, they will be doing so in Ralph Lauren - and blue jeans.\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9972163040212632, \"rank\": 0.0023290638960260317, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.8659175118148131, \"rank\": 0.1548444122630703, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, the designer unveiled the new look, billing the blazer and jean pairing as \\\"unexpected\\\" yet classic.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The look features tapered jeans, single-breasted wool blazers that come with red-and-white tipping, a blue-and-white striped Oxford shirt, and cream suede buck lace-up shoes.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oxford shirt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For theclosing ceremony, the team will wear white, moto-style denim jeans with matching jackets designed in patriotic red, white and blue.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA outfits for the upcoming 2024 Paris Olympic Games, including opening and closing ceremony apparel, are displayed at the Ralph Lauren Madison avenue headquarters in New York on June 17, 2024.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9972163040212632, \"rank\": 0.0023290638960260317, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999998376404297, \"rank\": 1.5918037879865884e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Credit: Charly TRIBALLEAU / AFP) (Photo by CHARLY  This is Lauren's ninth turn creating a look for Americans at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"David Lauren,the company's chief branding and innovation officer and its founder's son, told The Associated Press that he was unbothered by the casualness of blue denim.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999200427571111, \"rank\": 0.0008002122415529063, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We work very closely with Team USA to make the athletes feel at once dressed up, feel like a team, but at the same time comfortable and very distinctively American,\\\" he told The Associated Press on Monday during a media preview at the company's New York headquarters.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9972163040212632, \"rank\": 0.0023290638960260317, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999200427571111, \"rank\": 0.0008002122415529063, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999998376404297, \"rank\": 1.5918037879865884e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nothing says America like blue jeans, especially when we are in Paris,\\\" Lauren added.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999986944204, \"rank\": 1.3055009022571854e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it gives the athletes a chance to feel a sense of a culture but also feel like themselves and what is natural.\\\"\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media users may not have fully appreciated the logo, but the three-part design is steeped in significant meaning.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company also designed Team USA gear available for sale starting Tuesday at RalphLauren.com, TeamUSAShop.com and company stores in the U.S. and France.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1800, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9972163040212632, \"rank\": 0.0023290638960260317, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.98690081584123, \"rank\": 0.01121433195910256, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the wares on offer are polo shirts made of 100% recycled cotton.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first time Ralph Lauren has achieved thatlevel of sustainabilityin Olympic gear, David Lauren said.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.8659175118148131, \"rank\": 0.1548444122630703, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some proceeds of retail sales go to help support U.S. athletes training for their Olympic moments.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lauren would not be more specific on how much money the company sends their way.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED:Gymnastics star Gabby Douglas pulls out of US Championships, ending her bid for a third Olympics  The opening and closing ceremony uniforms, the same for the Olympics andsubsequent Paralympics,were made in the U.S.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2315, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabby Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Douglas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gear on sale to the public was made in both the U.S. and other countries.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games will be one of the biggest events ever organized in France and will take place from July 26 to August 11, 2024.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.5184012445239787e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999973944302222, \"rank\": 2.121000597674174e-06, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": 